videos.headline: Nobody's more excited for football's return than this guy
videos.description: Charlotte linebacker Peter Agabe is so pumped for football that he is flopping all over the field.

videos.headline: App State capitalizes on Charlotte defender slipping, score long TD
videos.description: A Charlotte defender slips leaving Appalachian State WR Thomas Hennigan wide open for a 51-yard touchdown.
